column5: Morning all, hope everyone had a great week, even if it was a little wet.  The tribs and rivers should be flowing good so if you're heading out    watch your step .  If you're heading out of town, have a great weekend and don't forget the camera, and if you're working, that's ok, just means you have a weekeday to be on the water while everyone else is at work  Enjoy Maureen
Good Morning Maureen....  I'm working another half day, done by 11 am.... then one more sleep till we get our new boat...  Have a great day..
